/images/2022/08/pwa_yummy_recipes_android_chrome_add_to_homescreen_hu_9cc74e8fecd2a9c4.webp" type=image/webp><img src=/images/2022/08/pwa_yummy_recipes_android_chrome_add_to_homescreen.jpg alt="PWA of Yummy Recipes on Android with information in Google Chrome about possibility to add to Home Screen" decoding=async width=657 height=1438 loading=lazy></picture></a></p><p>As I am not using any Android device, I did my test using <a href=https://www.lambdatest.com target=_blank rel=noopener>LabmdaTest.com</a>.</p><blockquote><p>Real-Time Testing > Browser Testing > Android, Samsung, Galaxy S20, Google Chrome.</p></blockquote><hr><p>On iOS and iPadOS we will not have such prompts. We need to use Share Sheet to add our app to Home Screen.</p><p><a href=/images/2022/08/ios_add_pwa_to_home_screen_sharesheet.jpg><picture><source media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/images/2022/08/ios_add_pwa_to_home_screen_sharesheet_hu_6d46e8440e4f7635.webp 2x,
